# Exploration: cat

## Rounds
  round 0: 38 isolated cumulative, 15 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 38 isolated cumulative, 15 identical in round (refinement)

## Distinguished: 10/10 flags
  10 solo (unique behavior)

Aliases: -A = --show-all, -E = --show-ends, -T = --show-tabs, -b = --number-nonblank, -n = --number, -s = --squeeze-blank, -v = --show-nonprinting

## Solo (unique behavior)
  -A  # equivalent to -vET
  -E  # display $ at end of each line
  -T  # display TAB characters as ^I
  -b  # number nonempty output lines, overrides -n
  -e  # equivalent to -vE
  -n  # number all output lines
  -s  # suppress repeated empty output lines
  -t  # equivalent to -vT
  -u  # (ignored)
  -v  # use ^ and M- notation, except for LFD and TAB

